The paper is about streaming volumetric media for augmented reality, which involves computer graphics (GR), multimedia (MM), computer vision (CV), networking (NI), and human-computer interaction (HC). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.GR, followed by cs.MM, cs.CV, cs.NI, and cs.HC.
